The following tools are necessary for building most output formats of the
design document (and other DocBook documentation) from their XML sources:

- GNU make
- dblatex
  dblatex has a number of dependences:
  - Python >= 2.4
  - Recent LaTeX distribution
  - xsltproc
  - XML DocBook 4.1 DTD
- Ghostscript
- groff + GNU pic
- HTML Tidy

